	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Things 3 Command Center — Capture, navigate, plan, and automate.

Keywords:
  do {task}        - Quick capture (modifiers: @today @tonight @tomorrow @someday !deadline #tag)
  things           - Navigate views and Areas
  find {query}     - Search Things
  plan {name}      - Create project (optional: plan Name / Task 1, Task 2)
  brainstorm {goal} - AI decomposes goal into full Things project (needs API key)
  routine          - Fire routine templates (Weekly Review, Morning Launch, etc.)

Setup:
  ANTHROPIC_API_KEY  - Your Anthropic API key (for brainstorm)
  THINGS_AUTH_TOKEN  - Your Things URL scheme auth token
  MODEL              - Claude model (default: claude-sonnet-4-20250514)</string>
